	<h2> CSS TAGS!!!!!</h2>
	<h4> COLOR</h4>
		
		<p> color= selects the color of the text</p>
	
	<h4> BACKGROUND</h4>

		<p> background-attachment= Sets whether of not a background picture is fixed or scrolls with the webpage</p>
		<p> background-color= specifies the color of the background</p>
		<p> background-image= specifies the image that'll be in the background</p>
		<p> background-position= specifies the placement of the background image</p>
		<p> background-size= specifies the size of the background image</p>
	
	<h4> BASIC BOX</h3>
		
			<p> height= sets the height</p>
			<p> margin= sets all margin properties(for specifics you can use margin-left, margin-right, margin-top, margin-bottom)</p>
			<p> padding= sets all of the padding properties(for specifics you can use padding-left, padding-right, padding-top, padding-bottom)</p>
			<p> width= sets the width</p>
			<p> postion= specifies the type of postitioning method used for an element (static, relative, absolute, fixed)</p>
			<p> .my-button= creates a button</p>

	<h4> FONT</h4>
	
			<p> font-family= specifies the family of the text</p>
			<p> font-size= specifies the size of the font</p>
			<p> font-weight= specifies the weight of the font</p>

			
		


